docs {
  ## Get Location
  ดึงข้อมูลสถานที่/คลังสินค้ารายการเดียวตาม ID

  Retrieves a single location/warehouse record by its unique identifier.


  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "uuid",
      "code": "LOC-001",
      "name": "Main Store",
      "location_type": "store",
      "is_active": true
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-27T00:00:00.000Z"
  }
  ```
}

params:path {
  id: {{location_id}}
}
